import React from 'react'
import { SidebarContainer, Icon, CloseIcon } from './SidebarElement';

const Sidebar = () => {
  return (
    <SidebarContainer>
        <Icon>
            <CloseIcon />
        </Icon>
        <SidebarWrapper>
          <SibebarMenu>
            <SidebarLink to="about">
              Sobre
            </SidebarLink>
            <SidebarLink to="discover">
              Discover
            </SidebarLink>
            <SidebarLink to="services">
              Services
            </SidebarLink>
            <SidebarLink to="signup">
              Sign Up
            </SidebarLink>
          </SibebarMenu>
          <SibedarBtnWrap>
            <SidebarRoute>Sign Up</SidebarRoute>

          </SibedarBtnWrap>
        </SidebarWrapper>
    </SidebarContainer>
  )
}

export default Sidebar
